的快乐手段，但是多巴胺知识快乐的承诺，这就会让虚伪的快乐和真实的紧张交织在一起，让你更加痛苦。<br>所以你应该主动完成紧急事项，，从源头解决压力。压力要是太大，用运动、冥想、听音乐这种积极的缓解方式放松。","like_count":3},{"had_liked":false,"id":298092,"user_name":"Super Ollie","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1429336,"ip_address":"","ucode":"4F30DE41673C97","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/15/cf/58/dabb0f73.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1623909657,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"14508811545","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"说出了很多我生活中遇到的矛盾事情，很不错！","like_count":3},{"had_liked":false,"id":298861,"user_name":"Geek_gong1zu","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2086659,"ip_address":"","ucode":"D629A6652AB8E2","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1f/d7/03/db060811.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1624347708,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"10214282300","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"1、当思想走神的时候，要意识到自己正在走神，尝试记下它<br>2、与压力共处，偶尔的“堕落”不要紧，要坚持下去，不能不断的批评自己，要自我谅解","like_count":2},{"had_liked":false,"id":298773,"user_name":"墨鱼","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1244755,"ip_address":"","ucode":"8919C16C8828DE","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/fe/53/a19bdb18.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1624324097,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"10214258689","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"给玩手机的时间设置时间限制","like_count":2},{"had_liked":false,"id":311448,"user_name":"欢乐的小马驹","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1078951,"ip_address":"","ucode":"B594106688CEE7","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/76/a7/374e86a7.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1631240040,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5926207336","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"每次一看到打个栗子，就不舒服，虽然这不是重点。我还得有意识提醒自己，这不是重点。但就是不舒服，就不能好好说话。非要自作聪明，把自以为是的俏皮话私货，用在这里？！！！","like_count":2},{"had_liked":false,